dct_title_s: Williams' map of the boroughs of Manhattan and the Bronx
dct_alternative_sm: Map of boroughs of Manhattan and the Bronx
dct_description_sm: Indexes to piers, rail road terminals, ferries, parks and museums.
Legend shows various rail and subway lines (under construction and in operation), ferries.
Bottom of map: "Williams Map of Boroughs of Manhattan and the Bronx ; Copyring 1911, by Williams Map & Guide Co. Corrected ug. 1915 Corrected Aug. 1916."
